{"tid":692602,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"阿 嬌 同 老 公 「 黑 白 配 」 抵 港","createTime":"2018-06-06T21:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T05:16:27.000Z","uid":37396,"like":51,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"e1e2151243e2dfd19bc08eb49293a4ccf3dc9562","tid":692602,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T21:48:23.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】剛榮升賴太的鍾欣潼（阿嬌），晚上7時許與老公賴弘國（Michael）返港。以「<span style=\"color: navy;\">黑</span><span style=\"color: pink;\">白</span>配」帽子Look上陣的二人，十指緊扣出閘，更不時對望甜笑。雖然二人邊行邊做訪問，仍應要求大騷閃爆婚戒，Michael 更戴上由阿嬌送的「生日金撈」，可惜婉拒錫錫晒恩愛，最後齊齊上車離開，約８時便返抵阿嬌位於西環的寓所「維壹」。<br />\n<br />\n問到阿嬌是「賴太」還是「準賴太」？阿嬌澄清美國之行並非簽紙註冊：「我們一起不算耐，但想有個美好的共同回憶，以及跟親朋好友共聚的片段，所以美國的婚禮片段也會在香港的婚禮播出，香港婚禮則在12月舉行，日子未定，因為仍未找到地方。雖然我很懶，加上香港婚禮找了專人負責，但我也花了很多心機呢，哈哈！」阿嬌解釋美國婚禮並非由老闆楊受成贊助，香港婚禮才是，問到楊生承諾送她物業，她認為老闆一定說話算話。她又謂蜜月去了很多地方，包括美國、日本及台灣，感謝公司放她長假，而老公是專誠陪她返港，明天便離開。<br />\n<br />\n問到老公值多少分？阿嬌說：「我不可以給他滿分，怕他驕傲。」記者問老公值90分嗎？阿嬌即說「值」。Michael即大讚阿嬌是滿分太太，更自爆連爸爸亦很喜歡阿嬌，給她滿分，因為阿嬌常常來台探望其家人，阿嬌識做回應說：「我也很喜歡他。（指賴父）」雖然家人有問過他們的生育計劃，但Michael溫柔地說要一步步來，阿嬌亦附和指生B要看緣份：「兩邊家人也沒有催，有壓力就生不到呢！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/07/054646_b5abd5c12ae11e72a2007a97fc3f12c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F054646_b5abd5c12ae11e72a2007a97fc3f12c1.jpg&h=29725337&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E9%98%BF%E5%AC%8C%E5%90%8C%E8%80%81%E5%85%AC-%E9%BB%91%E7%99%BD%E9%85%8D-%E6%8A%B5%E6%B8%AF-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A9%9A%E7%A6%AE12%E6%9C%88%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C-121100609.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.celebrity.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2598%25BF%25E5%25AC%258C%25E5%2590%258C%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%2585%25AC-%25E9%25BB%2591%25E7%2599%25BD%25E9%2585%258D-%25E6%258A%25B5%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A9%259A%25E7%25A6%25AE12%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%25A1%258C-121100609.html&d=qIAbQZyuGOXVpkIC6F%2FZ8EbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=6340daab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E9%98%BF%E5%AC%8C%E5%90%8C%E8%80%81%E5%85%AC-%E9%BB%91%E7%99%BD%E9%85%8D-%E6%8A%B5%E6%B8%AF-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A9%9A%E7%A6%AE12%E6%9C%88%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C-121100609.html</a>"},{"pid":"5dcb0632ee131ebcaa43a8687fe180c0c4c9c693","tid":692602,"uid":44160,"like":330,"dislike":2,"score":328,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T21:49:17.000Z","msg":"老公係白虎？"},{"pid":"0590767a4222022bf1e2fc2117a9e828a6f08b54","tid":692602,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T22:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e63d396819803e217d180ee8cf15d6acd906a04","tid":692602,"uid":5190,"like":43,"dislike":5,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T22:20:17.000Z","msg":"呀嬌好白<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6599f211d28720241a96e7cf1796a6bd2785853b","tid":692602,"uid":3936,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T22:21:05.000Z","msg":"黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc778f0d2d768453541b45dd3e9a9d9fbad4ca21","tid":692602,"uid":82747,"like":129,"dislike":14,"score":115,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T22:21:53.000Z","msg":"個樣仲咁後生咁靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a7e04c1bcb62e03a1688b9e6982e9b5218b1087","tid":692602,"uid":38049,"like":131,"dislike":39,"score":92,"quote":{"pid":"9e63d396819803e217d180ee8cf15d6acd906a04","tid":692602,"uid":5190,"like":43,"dislike":5,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T22:20:17.000Z","msg":"呀嬌好白<img src=